20L.F.summary: Bong AB (publ) manufactures and sells specialty packaging and envelope products. It provides solutions for distribution and packaging of information, advertising materials, and lightweight goods. The company offers envelopes, gift packaging, carrier bags for the retail trade, and packaging for e-commerce. It also provides light packaging products, including covers for lightweight goods; expanders and pockets, such as kraft paper, bubble mailers, paper padded bags, all board mailers, and cardboard packaging, as well as ColdSeal, a corrugated material with specially designed latex coating on the inside. The company has operations in Sweden, Norway, Denmark, Finland, Estonia, the United Kingdom, Belgium, Germany, France, Poland, Spain, Switzerland, Russia, Romania, Italy, and Tunisia. Bong AB (publ) was founded in 1737 and is headquartered in Kristianstad, Sweden.
